<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We invite you to read Forrester’s <a href="https://content.pivotal.io/analyst-reports/reduce-risk-and-improve-security-through-infrastructure-automation?utm_source=pivotal-email&amp;utm_medium=email-link&amp;utm_campaign=email-forrester-reduce-risk-q318" target="_blank" style="color: #00ae9e; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 400;">Reduce Risk And Improve Security Through Infrastructure Automation</a> report.</span></p> 
<p><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">According to Forrester, today's security initiatives are impossible to execute manually. As infrastructure-as-code (IaC), edge computing, and internet-of-things (IoT) solutions proliferate, organizations must leverage automation to protect their business technology strategies. It can be tempting to continue the I&amp;O and security and risk processes that have seemingly worked for years...but doing so puts your business and customers at severe risk. Automation is a profoundly effective movement that will revolutionize I&amp;O professionals' work.</span></p> 
<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Read this report and learn how infrastructure and operations (I&amp;O) and security professionals can deliver efficient risk management and compliance throughout the entire solution stack — with unprecedented speed, agility, and dependability. </span></p> 
<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span><br></p> 
